{"tid":1537913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九月六日，全民戴裝日！","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:57:25.000Z","uid":47541,"like":292,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"cc33eb4d0a014830315fd8c6b3afbf32944ee8a3","tid":1537913,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"[轉貼]<br />\n<br />\n9月6號，全民戴裝日<br />\n<br />\n目的係提醒大家行街坐車都會隨時被襲擊，扑頭、噴椒、或身處毒霧環境，所以要戴上防具作象徵，靜默地抗議。<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點提議比番大家:<br />\n1. 番學番工放工時間做，越多人做效果越好，人多亦唔易比人check身份證<br />\n2. 行街坐車行商場都戴住，唔使怕奇怪，因為更無理既事日日都發生緊<br />\n3. 番工裝扮未必帶到頭盔，但唔戴都帶住，作為一個象徵，又或者只帶口罩眼罩<br />\n4. 真勇武就小心，比人check身份證留record就麻煩<br />\n5. 只帶防具，只係要保護自己，唔好有其他可疑裝備<br />\n<br />\n當人人都有頭盔口罩係身既時候，就可以淡化帶gear本身既奇怪，保護大家，亦比一份支持勇武。"},{"pid":"850ca6698e52e7271d958a37ddeee159161992e6","tid":1537913,"uid":47541,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKKkYS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKKkYS8.jpg&h=8f67b3ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2005bd57887c26d2507741cb722fc129d68fe43d","tid":1537913,"uid":47541,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOixPZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOixPZT.jpg&h=429e99ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"758d84a52ddb1e3137cb4fbd3146587701c2f738","tid":1537913,"uid":47541,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzJqqyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzJqqyp.jpg&h=5314d411&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b594e4026d8327513f3eee5f6fdd2fb1e4db618","tid":1537913,"uid":47541,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsakerW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi