\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈內容包括：</span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b1ae61753e9c2ef56e9c756bc6c6fbb6f9159c54","tid":1537913,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"先推全民口罩日先"},{"pid":"1cf90c7eb35dffc614255c699219f67476b30568","tid":1537913,"uid":166591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"850ca6698e52e7271d958a37ddeee159161992e6","tid":1537913,"uid":47541,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKKkYS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKKkYS8.jpg&h=8f67b3ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"：香港人<br />\n：獨立！"},{"pid":"b35af5c5de358e1b3acb8589c76499d8052c72e8","tid":1537913,"uid":39855,"lik